'''Project Haven''' was commissioned by [[Alliance High Command/Legends|Alliance High Command]] following the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]]. Its goal was to scour [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] for new safe worlds to use as headquarters. The thousands of worlds discovered included [[Hoth/Legends|Hoth]] and [[Da Soocha V|Pinnacle Moon]].

After the [[Liberation of Coruscant (Galactic Civil War)|Liberation of Coruscant]], many in the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] wanted to symbolically burn the Project Haven files, but they were kept as a precautionary measure. However, the safe-world list was largely compromised by agents of [[Mitth'raw'nuruodo/Legends|Thrawn]].

